		{
			"eventType": "group",
			"disabled": false,
			"title": "Player",
			"description": "",
			"isActiveOnStart": true,
			"children": [
				{
					"eventType": "comment",
					"text": "Every tick of execution (60 FPS = 60 times in a second) the actions are executed.\nHere we position the PlayerAnim object to the object PlayerBox's position. The PlayerBox is the \"hitbox\" that the other game pieces interact with, while the \"PlayerAnim\" is the artwork that sits on top of the hitbox. \nWe also have our txtScore object displaying the value of the Score global variable."
				},
				{
					"eventType": "block",
					"conditions": [
						{
							"id": "every-tick",
							"objectClass": "System",
							"sid": 633674518974393
						}
					],
					"actions": [
						{
							"id": "set-position-to-another-object",
							"objectClass": "PlayerAnim",
							"sid": 750366818675508,
							"parameters": {
								"object": "PlayerBox",
								"image-point-optional": "0"
							}
						},
						{
							"id": "set-text",
							"objectClass": "txtScore",
							"sid": 178251763777476,
							"parameters": {
								"text": "\"Score: \" & Score"
							}
						}
					],
					"sid": 220350709480750
				},
				{
					"eventType": "comment",
					"text": "When pressing the left or right key of the keyboard, we mirror (or not) the PlayerAnim object in order to have the animation facing the correct direction."
				},
				{
					"eventType": "block",
					"conditions": [
						{
							"id": "on-key-pressed",
							"objectClass": "Keyboard",
							"sid": 727474870702857,
							"parameters": {
								"key": 37
							}
						}
					],
					"actions": [
						{
							"id": "set-mirrored",
							"objectClass": "PlayerAnim",
							"sid": 226153253560423,
							"parameters": {
								"state": "mirrored"
							}
						}
					],
					"sid": 614059646124724
				},
				{
					"eventType": "block",
					"conditions": [
						{
							"id": "on-key-pressed",
							"objectClass": "Keyboard",
							"sid": 104913481357692,
							"parameters": {
								"key": 39
							}
						}
					],
					"actions": [
						{
							"id": "set-mirrored",
							"objectClass": "PlayerAnim",
							"sid": 991720859176926,
							"parameters": {
								"state": "not-mirrored"
							}
						}
					],
					"sid": 172169328167677
				},
